overview: More Lost & Found can be found on “Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 13”! That’s right, lucky number 13 brings you Jello Biafra running for mayor of San Francisco, the C.I.A.’s quest for mind control, whacko movie footage & strange commercials from across the globe, musical performances from Black Sabbath, Geto Boys, Gang of Four, 999, The Searchers & Lou Reed, mind melting animation, Redd Foxx, Andy Kaufman, public access conspiracists, a grim depiction of Hell, Tracy Smothers wrestling a bear with the great Gordon Solie calling the “match”, and SO much more!
title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 13
